name: Teleporter (itch) (ZbamGames)
description: Theme; There And Back: You are on first dimension, but there is another dimension too.You can go there and back using E key Controls: Move : A-D or Arrow keys Jump : W-Space-Up Arrow See Other Dimension : Q Teleport Other Dimension : E Pause&Resume : Escape How To Play: You control ball on a world and it can travel between 2 dimensions while travelling or observing other dimension, you consume your berries.To gain berries.You should get cherries.Mushrooms all over the world will give you random effect.Your goal is to reach end on every level.
